{"id":9059,"content":"<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">有读者询问《炎黄春秋》杂志近几年的合订本是否有售。现统一答复如下：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">目前，本刊的合订本仅存有</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2010</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年和</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年两种。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本会在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月份面市。在此三年以前的合订本本社发行部已无存书。如市面上不会有也不应该有成批量发售《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2009</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年以前（含</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2009</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年）各年度的合订本，因为本刊发行部是《炎黄春秋》杂志各年度合订本的惟一发行渠道。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">目前，本刊</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2010</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本尚有少量存书，均为上下两册，每套定价</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">105</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元，欲购从速。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">本刊</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本共分两种：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><BR><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、简装两册合订本（上下册）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">定价</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">120</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><BR><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、简装一册合订本</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">定价</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">110</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.0gd\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">（说明：上下两册合订本便于翻阅和携带）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">本刊</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本将在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月份面市，届时本网会在第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">时间公告读者。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、邮局汇款：欲订购本刊合订本的读者，请通过邮局直接将款项邮寄本刊发行部，并在汇款单上填写收件人详细地址、邮编、姓名、要求及联系电话。合订本邮购免收邮费。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28.05pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.67gd\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、银行汇款：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">开户名：北京炎黄春秋杂志发行部</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">帐　号：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> 01090324900120109064325 <BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">开户行：北京银行复兴支行</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=E